author: COMSOL
description: The topology-optimized Tesla microvalve is used as inspiration for an initial geometry. Second-order Bernstein polynomials are used to perturb the shape of the geometry. The resulting design is remeshed in the deformed configuration and the performance is investigated for a range of Reynolds numbers.
label: tesla_microvalve_shape_optimization.mph
